hp_redis_cmd:
  profile: |-
    {{hyper_ibank_redis_config}}
  command: get
  args_mapping: root = [ this.redis_key ]
  input: |
    root = this

  result_mode: merge

  output: |
    root = {}
    root.strResult = this
nodes.name: Get by redis_key
